        .content
          h2 Alexandros Marinos, Rulemotion Ltd
          p Rob is one of those rare developers that combines excellent skill, communication ability, long-term technical vision, and justified confidence in his skills. 
          p During his time with us, we gave him a project that we hoped he would make some early progress on, and he proceeded to produce a working prototype. This project included having to learn an esoteric parsing language, for which he wrote a tutorial at the same time.
          p In addition, he left our organisation with some long-term improvements in our architecture and testing approach. I can hardly reccommend working with Rob more.
